"title": "6668: grace, and Jesus Christ",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6668",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Grace is demonstrated pre-eminently in Jesus Christ and the work he came to do.</p>\n<h2>God's promise of grace has been fulfilled in Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:16-John1:17\">JHN 1:16–1:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8-2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:8–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16-John3:17\">JHN 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:38\">ACT 13:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1-Rom1:5\">ROM 1:1–1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">ROM 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:16-Rom5:17\">ROM 5:16–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3-Eph1:8\">EPH 1:3–1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11-Titus2:14\">TIT 2:11–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:5\">TIT 3:4–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></p>\n<h2>Grace was expressed in Jesus Christ's life and ministry</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:34\">MRK 6:34</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:10-Matt9:13\">MAT 9:10–9:13</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:15-Mark2:17\">MRK 2:15–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27-Luke5:32\">LUK 5:27–5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:4-Matt11:5\">MAT 11:4–11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:15\">MAT 19:13–19:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:16\">MRK 10:13–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:15-Luke18:17\">LUK 18:15–18:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:40\">LUK 2:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:22\">LUK 4:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:9-Luke19:10\">LUK 19:9–19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">LUK 23:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11\">JHN 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:37-Acts10:38\">ACT 10:37–10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:9\">HEB 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a></p>\n<h2>Grace is demonstrated in Jesus Christ's atoning death on the cross</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:16-John1:17\">JHN 1:16–1:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:10\">1PE 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:22-Rom3:24\">ROM 3:22–3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:2\">ROM 5:1–5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:32\">ROM 8:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:4-1Cor1:6\">1CO 1:4–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:18-2Cor5:19\">2CO 5:18–5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:21\">GAL 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:7\">EPH 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:16-2Thess2:17\">2TH 2:16–2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:13-1Tim1:14\">1TI 1:13–1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:10\">1JN 4:10</a></p>",
